<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Invite to <%= @event.name %></h1>
    <p>
      <%= @inviter.username %> has invited you to a movie event.<br/>
    </p>
    <h3>How to respond</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Sign in <%= link_to "here", new_user_session_url %>.
      <li>Go to your home page from the "My Home" button on the sidebar or through the "My Festival" menu.
      <li>In the "Invitations" section just click "accept" or "decline" alongside the inviation.
    </ol>
    <p>You do not have to accept the invitation immediately. As an unconfirmed attendee you will still receive updates and be able to take part in the selection process.</p>
    <p>Enjoy the festival!</p>
    <p>Cheers,<br>GarageFilmFestival.org</p>
  </body>
</html>
